text: Wakool is a town in New South Wales, Australia Wakool may also refer to: *Wakool (ship), a ship of the Blue Anchor Line, which entered service in 1898 *Wakool River, an anabranch of the Edward River in the western Riverina region of south western New South Wales, Australia *Wakool Shire, formerly a local government area in the Riverina region of New South Wales, Australia *Wakool County, a cadastral divisions of New South Wales
title: Wakool (disambiguation)
